---
title: St.Jean Baptiste Cheesy Beyond Meat® Blueberry Burgers with Crispy Potato Wedges and Mustard-Mayo Dipper
description: Celebrate St. Jean Baptiste Day with a satisfying, summery Beyond Meat® burger! The flavour of sweet blueberry is paired with sharp whole grain mustard to make a saucy topping for this burger. It's completed with white cheddar, pickled onions and crispy potato wedges for summer vibes in every bite.
